msgid "Welcome Screen"
msgstr "Sgrin Croeso"

#: usr/lib/linuxmint/mintWelcome/mintWelcome.py:85
msgid ""
"Welcome and thank you for choosing Linux Mint. We hope you'll enjoy using it "
"as much as we did designing it. The links below will help you get started "
"with your new operating system. Have a great time and don't hesitate to send "
"us your feedback."
msgstr ""
"Croeso a diolch am ddewis Linux Mint. Rydym yn gobeithio y byddwch yn ei "
"fwynhau gymaint ag yr ydym wedi mwynhau ei gynllunio. Bydd y dolenni isod yn "
"eich cynorthwyo i gychwyn gyda'ch system weithredu newydd. Mwynhewch eich "
"hun a pheidiwch â phetruso ag anfon adborth atom."

